    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-08-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-08-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="427" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d427">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Runyon</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-08-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 20,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department informed that the Prussian Government on 16th instant, in
                            advance of expected discussion, revoked concession Mutual Life Insurance
                            Company, to take effect September 1. If this report be correct, you are
                            instructed strongly to represent injustice of proceeding in view of our
                            previous representations and of the willingness of company to confine
                            business in Prussia to plans approved by the Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
